com.mumfrey.liteloader.interfaces

Interface ObjectFactory<TClient,TServer extends MinecraftServer>

  • Type Parameters:
    TClient - Type of the client runtime, "Minecraft" on client and null on the server
    TServer - Type of the server runtime, "IntegratedServer" on the client, "MinecraftServer" on the server

    public interface ObjectFactory<TClient,TServer extends MinecraftServer>
    Factory for generating loader managament objects based on the environment
